	('B00B9LNOKM', 'An animated series based on the popular children''s toy &#34;Digimon&#34;, in which kids raise electronic monsters to fight against those raised by other kids. The show follows the adventures of a team of real monster trainers as they travel about honing their skills and facing challenges from rival trainers.'),
	('B00B9LNOKM', 'Brian Keith Beacock (born March 29, 1966 in Hayward, California, USA) is an American television and film actor and a voice actor in anime and video games. He is perhaps best known for playing Byonko in Zatch Bell!, Takato Matsuki in Digimon Tamers, and Yamato Delgado in Battle B-Daman.'),
	('B00B9LNOKM', 'Bridget Hoffman is an American voice actress, ADR director and script writer in the Los Angeles area who works with Bang Zoom! Entertainment. She has provided voices for a number of English language versions of Japanese anime films and television series, usually under an alias such as Ruby Marlowe, Serena Kolb, or Tessa Ariel. Some of her notable roles include Belldandy in some of the early Oh My Goddess films, Mizuho Kazami in Please Teacher, and Shinobu Maehara in Love Hina.'),
	('B00B9LNOKM', 'Melissa Fahn (born April 28, 1973) is an American voice/stage actress and singer for anime dubs, cartoon series, Broadway and Los Angeles Theatre.'),
	('B00BGQWM3U', 'Germany, 1943, B&W, 89 minutes. Directed by M. W. Kimmich. Starring Peter Petersen, Luis Trenker, Lotte Koch, Albert Lippert. German dialogue, Optional English subtitles.<br> <b> WARNING: contains scenes of female nudity.</b>'),
	('B00C6WHQKW', 'Cuban America explores the continuing Cuban-American story as a concentrated exile group''s impact on transforming the sleepy, tourist town of Miami into a major, metropolitan community. A detailed look into the complex experience of Cuban-Americans of who they are, how they came to be, where they came from, where they are going, what they did, and, more importantly, how they are portrayed.'),
	('B00DCRE87O', 'The compelling true story of the charismatic Ward Allen, who in the early 1900s leaves behind a life of privilege in Savannah to live off the land with his hunting buddy Christmas Moultrie and must choose between his newfound freedom and the love a the society woman who captures his heart.'),
	('B00DYEBLYI', '<h4>Product Description</h4><br>'),
	('B00DYEBLYI', 'Digifans unite! The first four seasons of Digimon are together for the first time on DVD! Over 73 hours of your favorite episodes Digivolve into one amazing collection.'),
	('B00DYEBLYI', 'This dynamic 32-DVD set brings you 205 episodes of the Digimon series starting with DIGIMON ADVENTURE and DIGIMON ADVENTURE 02, the classic seasons that started it all, and DIGIMON TAMERS and DIGIMON FRONTIER, the continuation of the series with all new characters and worlds.'),
	('B00DYEBLYI', 'Relive your favorite moments with Tai and the original Digidestined, journey back to the DigiWorld with Davis and the new class of chosen kids, follow Takato a mega fan of the Digimon Card Game into the Digital World for the first time, or join Takuya as he learns the history of Spirits and Ancient Warriors.'),
	('B00DYEBLYI', 'Character guides | Photo Galleries'),
	('B00E27NH1G', 'Germany, 1940, B&W, 100 mins. Directed by Eduard von Borsody. Starring Ilse Werner, Carl Raddatz. German dialogue, Optional English subtitles. <P><B>Bonus Material:</B> Historical Slideshow.'),
	('B00FGG60XY', 'Touching and funny story of the many perfect ways that love can be expressed. --Sarasota Film Festival<br /><br />Instead of preaching about marriage equality, The Perfect Wedding simply shows life in futuristic world where it s taken for granted. And that world looks pretty good. --Herald-Tribune Heartwarming... illustrating a fresh take on a modern family. --This Week in Sarasota<br /><br />Heartwarming... illustrating a fresh take on a modern family. --This Week in Sarasota'),
	('B00FXP69O8', 'Kylee Nash is the biggest star on the late night cable horizon.'),
	('B00FXP69O8', 'Her screen credits include the films The Hills Have Thighs, Busty Coeds Vs. Lusty Cheerleaders, Knock Outs, Rewind Time Machine and Super Shark.'),
	('B00FXP69O8', 'In this sequel to DOUBLE TROUBLE, DOUBLE TROUBLE 2, Kylee Nash stars again in 8 new and never-before-seen scenes from your favorite late-night fantasies!'),
	('B00GOT1DNO', 'NewVideoGroup have done it again, they are going to release the second season of digimon which is one of my favorite seasons. --Rave Mystery<br /><br />Now we can see all . . . episodes of it in this soon-to-be-a-hit DVD set! --ToonXpert87<br /><br />I enjoy watching it still it''s fun, cartoony, and sometimes so over the top its still worth the watch. --TheNerdCollector'),
	('B00GOYHS1K', '<![CDATA['),
	('B00GOYHS1K', 'WWE: Shawn Michaels: Mr. WrestleMania (3-Disc)(DVD)'),
	('B00GOYHS1K', 'For 30 years, every WWE Superstar has laced up their boots with one goal in mind, stealing the show at WrestleMania, but only one man has earned the nickname, Mr. WrestleMania. Now, relive every singles and tag team match from the Heartbreak Kid at the event that made him The Icon.'),
	('B00GX7WNA4', 'Three Teleplays all written by ''''Twilight Zone'''' creator Rod Serling. Includes ''''Nightmare At Ground Zero,'''' ''''The Arena,'''' and ''''A Town Has Turned To Dust'''' (with William Shatner and Rod Steiger).<P>Includes long lost interviews with Rod Serling.'),
	('B00HFC90TI', 'Kai and Aki dream of building a giant fighting robot based on a super-popular anime, but thats going to be impossible if they dont get more members into their schools Robot Research Club. Theyll take anyone they can talkor forceinto joining them, including an eccentric robotics champion with a secret identity and a l33t video-game designer whos spent one too many late nights online. Finally, their goal looks like its within reach.'),
	('B00HFC90TI', 'But when a sentient AI program tells Kai about mysterious documents hidden on the internet, things start to get strange for everyone. As the club members track down the secret messages, they realize that the information might be far biggerand more dangerousthan they expected.'),
	('B00HXEWGY4', 'Relive the classic era of anime with the studio that brought you Escaflowne, Fullmetal Alchemist, and Wolfs Rain. Eureka Seven, the greatest anime love story ever told, returns to the spotlight after almost a decadein a complete series collection for the first time!'),
	('B00HXEWGY4', 'Backed by its original powerhouse vocal cast, Eureka Seven is a series that demonstrates what anime should be (Random Curiosity)'),
	('B00HXEWG0S', 'Fall in love alongside Renton and Eureka all over again with this feature film set in an alternate timeline within the Eureka Seven universe!'),
	('B00KQ05T8C', '<b>JULIE STRAIN, MONIQUE GABRIELLE and JULIE K. SMITH IN FULL 1920 X 1080 HD!</b>'),
	('B00KQ05T8C', 'We took the best scenes from our most popular models and converted* them to <b>HIGH DEFINITION</b> from the highest quality original elements.'),
	('B00KQ05T8C', 'In our opinion <b>THE RESULTS WERE ASTONISHING!</b>'),
	('B00KQ05T8C', 'The kind of close-up realism that only <b>HIGH DEFINITION BLU-RAY</b> can deliver.'),
	('B00KQ05T8C', '*While this disc is in full 1920 X 1080 resolution, in order to preserve quality the scenes are presented in their original 4 X 3 aspect ratio.'),
