	('B00NQ2SEBG', 'Biore deep pore charcoal cleanser targets deep-down impurities to defend against daily buildup - like dirt, oil and make-up - for a truly deep clean. Naturally purifies and deep cleans. Draws out and traps 2x more dirt and impurities than a basic cleanser. Provides deeply cleaned, tingly-smooth skin. Contains natural charcoal.'),
	('B00NQ2SEBG', 'Work like a magnet to draw out and trap deep down dirt, oil &amp; impurities while also absorbing excess oil. Great for oily skin.'),
