	('B00NQ2P7AC', 'Ideal for normal-to-dry skin types, Lubriderm Daily Moisture Lotion helps replenish and moisturize dry skin. From a dermatologist-developed brand, this hydrating lotion is clinically shown to help moisturize for a full 24 hours. The lotion is enriched with vitamin B5 and essential moisturizers naturally found in healthy skin to improve skin''s moisture barrier. Great for smoothing over hands and body every day, Lubriderm Daily Moisture Lotion is non-greasy for a clean, pleasant feel on the skin.'),
	('B00NQ2NI2G', 'Helps even tone and texture for radiant-looking skin.'),
	('B00NQ2NI2G', 'Traditional Chinese medicine has used soy for thousands of years to reduce the appearance of blotchy skin and discoloration. Aveeno scientists devised a way to process soybeans that retains the integrity of the proteins to help provide immediate and long-term skin benefits. Products with our Active Naturals Total Soy Complex visibly transform dull, uneven skin into brighter, more radiant skin.'),
	('B00NQ2NI2G', 'From humble beginnings in 1945, the story of the Aveeno Brand has been one of discovery. By unlocking natures powers through scientific advances, they have discovered ways to nurture and transform skin and hair to an enhanced state of natural health and beauty.'),
	('B00NQ2TZEQ', 'Collagen is an essential natural protein that works with elastin to keep your skin supple, taut and looking young. As we age, collagen deteriorates as skin begins to loose its moisture. The skin&#039;s surface becomes uneven, skin loses its cushion, and wrinkles form.'),
	('B00NQ2TZEQ', 'Now, Collagen Moisture Filler with powerful Natural Collagen provides a daily dose of intense hydration that helps fill in lines and wrinkles and restores moisture for smoother, more cushioned skin.'),
	('B00NQ2TZEQ', 'A dose of intense hydration and natural collagen in Collagen Moisture Filler Day/ Night Cream is essential for younger-looking skin. Rich moisture instantly restores skins cushion and bounce. Over time, the powerful natural collagen helps fill in lines and wrinkles, leaving your skin smooth and plump. Use it for a complete collagen-infused skincare regimen.'),
	('B00NQ2TZEQ', 'How to use: Every night, smooth gently over the entire face.'),
