	('B00TIROVCY', 'Bai Bubbles Gimbi Pink Grapefruit is a refreshing sparkling antioxidant infused drink with a fruity kick and only 5 calories and 1 gram of sugar per can. This effervescent and flavorful beverage is free of artificial sweeteners, so you can leave sugary sodas and unwanted sweeteners behind. Infused with antioxidants and loaded with bright taste, Bai Bubbles Gimbi Pink Grapefruit is a smart way to add some flavorful bubbles to your life.'),
	('B00TIROVCY', 'Using a powerhouse superfruit-the coffeefruit-Bai Bubbles are infused with antioxidants. Antioxidants give an extra electron to free radicals, which are caused by pollution, UV radiation, x-rays, stress, and/or strenuous exercise. This extra electron neutralizes the free radical and helps break the chain reaction of oxidation, which helps combat damage to the bodys cells.'),
	('B00TIROVCY', 'The secret to a flavored water that tastes so sweet but has only 5 calories per serving lies in Bai&#039;s Proprietary Sweetener Blend of erythritol and stevia leaf extract. Stevia leaf extract is more sweeter, so only a small amount is needed in the mix. Erythritol, which is found in fruits like pears and melons, is used to evenly disperse the intense sweetness of stevia leaf extract throughout the drink. The erythritol Bai uses is a sugar alcohol made from simple sugars.'),
	('B00TIROVCY', 'Bai works every day to make a world where doing what&#039;s right doesn&#039;t mean sacrificing enjoyment, where flavor and good feelings go hand in hand with no limits on taste, geography, or imagination. Bai sees beverages as an agent of change toward that world, and they started a &#039;bevolution&#039; to inspire people to rethink what they drink. It&#039;s a journey.'),
	('B00TIROVCY', 'Bai Bubbles sparkling antioxidant drinks are free of artificial sweeteners and have only 5 calories and 1 gram of sugar per serving, offering amazing flavor without the baggage associated with most carbonated drinks. When there&#039;s nothing more refreshing than a cold sparkling beverage, Bai Bubbles low calorie drinks will float your taste buds off to flavor heaven.'),
	('B00TIROVCY', 'Note: For more information please refer ingredients list.'),
	('B00TIROVCY', 'Enjoy Bai as a stand alone beverage, add some flavor to your cooking or even mix it in to your favorite cocktail or mocktail.'),
