	('B00TS9KZH2', 'CHEETOS snacks are the much-loved cheesy treats that are fun for everyone! You just cant eat a CHEETOS snack without licking the cheetle off your fingertips. And wherever the CHEETOS brand and CHESTER CHEETAH go, cheesy smiles are sure to follow.'),
	('B00UB6U1RU', 'You can smile confidently when you use Colgate Total Plus Whitening toothpaste. It not only offers the benefits of regular toothpaste but also refreshes and whitens teeth by gently removing surface stains. This teeth-whitening toothpaste is specially formulated to eliminate stains and fight against cavities, plaque and gingivitis while preventing the occurrence of new stains and tartar buildup.'),
	('B00UB6U1RU', '- Refreshes and whitens teeth by gently removing surface stains.'),
	('B00UB6U1RU', '- Fights germs for 12 hours.'),
	('B00UB6U1RU', '80% of bacteria in your mouth are not even on your teeth.'),
	('B00UB6U1RU', 'Colgate Total Advanced toothpaste protects all mouth surfaces teeth, tongue, cheeks, and gums. So 100% of your mouth surfaces get protected.'),
	('B00UB6U1RU', 'Reduces bacteria on teeth, tongue, cheeks and gums; helps prevent plaque, tartar and gingivitis, fortifies enamel. Not intended for prevention or treatment of more serious oral conditions.'),
	('B00UB6T2I4', 'Colgate Extra Clean Full Head Medium Toothbrush is designed with circular power bristles to help remove tooth stains. Its cleaning tip bristles effectively reach and clean back teeth and between teeth. This manual toothbrush also has an easy-to-grip handle to provide comfort and control while brushing. Remember to change your toothbrush every 3 months.'),
	('B00UB6X2IK', 'Over time, acids in your diet can soften your tooth enamel, making it more vulnerable to being worn away. That''s why there''s Pronamel Gentle Whitening toothpaste. It''s specially formulated to help protect enamel against the effects of acid erosion from everyday acidic foods and drinks such as wine, fruit, or soda. Plus, it both gently and effectively removes stains to help restore teeth to their natural whiteness.*'),
