	('B010FB5NRI', 'Caltrate 600 Plus D3 Plus Minerals offers a dual benefit formula to support strong, healthy bones.* Like all the Caltrate products you trust, Plus Minerals has calcium and the most vitamin D3 for bone strength.* Plus, there are added essential minerals including Zinc, Copper, and Manganese that help support bone flexibility, so you can continue to enjoy dancing, walking in the park or any of the activities you love.*'),
	('B010FB5NRI', 'You could say that collagen holds your whole body together. So supporting your body&#039;s collagen production is important in your overall bone health. That&#039;s why Caltrate 600 Plus D3 Plus Minerals offers calcium plus collagen-supporting minerals that help your bones stay strong and flexible.*'),
	('B010FB5NRI', 'Collagen is found in many places in your body including bones and muscles. Unfortunately as you get older, your body&#039;s ability to produce collagen begins to slow down and can impact your bone and muscle health. Caltrate 600 Plus D3 Plus Minerals has calcium plus collagen-supporting minerals to help your bones stay strong and flexible, so you can continue living the active life you love.'),
	('B010FB5NRI', 'Your bones need calcium to stay strong and healthy. When you do not get enough calcium in your diet, your body steals it from your bones. While getting calcium from food is ideal, many people don&#039;t get enough from diet alone. In fact, recent studies have shown just over half of U.S. women don&#039;t get enough calcium. Adding a calcium supplement, like Caltrate 600 Plus D3 Plus Minerals, to your daily routine can help replenish calcium in your body and maintain strong bones.*'),
