	('B0000CBIF4', 'Poulan 18-Inch Chain 3/8 #952051338. Poulan 18-inch saw chain features top performing Chamfer Chisel cutters and a notched bumper drive link for low kickback performance, good chip flow, and a smooth cutting action. The twin corners of the cutters chain deliver superior performance on the low profile 3/8-inch pitch chain.'),
	('B000BODU0W', 'This 9-in diameter square catch basin kit collects excess surface water from lawn, landscape, residential driveways and garages. The sump area collects debris and prevents clogged pipes. It features an ultraviolet-resistant one-piece injection-molded structural foam polyolefin for maximum strength. Full line of accessories available.'),
	('B000EOJWWO', 'The flag of Italy, often referred to in Italian as Il Tricolore, features three equally sized vertical bands of green, white and red, with the green at the hoist side. The first entity to use the Italian flag was the Cispadane Republic in 1796, after Napoleon''s army crossed Italy. During this time, many small republics based on the Jacobian model, were formed and almost all used the French tricolour with different colours.'),
