	('B00B2BZFO2', '<b>Features:</b> <br /> Wirelessly connect to any Bluetooth device <br /> Bluetooth enabled audio control functions <br /> Play music directly from Micro SD slot <br /> Built-in Li-Ion rechargeable battery <br /> Hands-free speaker phone function <br /> 6 to 8 hours Runtime <br /> Weight: 1 lb (w/box), 11 oz (speaker only) <br /> <br /> <b>Accessories:</b> <br /> USB Mini 5 pin cable (for charging) <br /> 3.5mm Audio cable (Aux input cable) <br /> User Manual <br />'),
