	('B00CJH0D1I', 'LCD & Digitizer Assembly 001/111 for BlackBerry Torch 9810 White'),
	('B00DXHJI0K', 'Our screen protectors are made from Optical Grade Crystal Film which are custom cut to ensure a perfect fit every time. Constructed in five layers; a scratch resistant surface polymer, a hardened protective mask to prevent deep cuts damaging your device and finally a patented silicone gel that creates a vacuum to securely ''cling'' to the device screen. Our screen protectors use no adhesive and there is no spraying anything to the protector or the device.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'The Nokia Lumia 925 is powered by 1.5GHz dual-core it comes with 1GB of RAM. The phone packs 16GB of internal storage cannot be expanded. As far as the cameras are concerned, the Nokia Lumia 925 packs a 8.7-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 1.2-megapixel front shooter for selfies.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'The polycarbonate body of the Nokia Lumia has been overhauled for the Nokia Lumia 925, with the robust metal frame providing a sleek, modern look as well as working as an antenna so you''ll be even more connected than before.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'The super-bright 4.5-inch AMOLED display offers great sunlight performance, and the enhanced responsiveness of the Super Sensitive touch-screen technology enables you to use it with your nails or gloves. It''s also protected from scratches by Corning''s Gorilla Glass 2.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'Running the Windows Phone 8 operating system, the Lumia 925 is powered by a 1.5 GHz dual-core processor and it features 16 GB of internal storage.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'Great looking images come easily when snapping them with the Lumia 925''s rear 8.7-megapixel PureView camera, which features a high-quality, wide angle Carl Zeiss lens and optical image stabilization (OIS). Using a floating lens, the Lumia 925 OIS feature compensates for and reduces movement in both videos and photos while also ensuring your photos look incredibly clear even in low-light situations. A powerful Xenon flash supplies even more light when you need it.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'The rear camera records stunning videos at up to Full HD 1080p resolution, and OIS reduces shakiness to make your videos much more pleasant to watch. The Lumia 925 also offers a front-facing camera for on-the-go video calls that can record up to HD 720p resolution.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'In addition to amazing imaging and video capabilities, the Lumia 925 offers rich distortion-free audio capture, even in noisy conditions. Built with three high-audio-amplitude-capture (HAAC) microphones, the Lumia 925 enables you to capture everything from the thumping bass of your favorite band to the delighted laugh of a playing child with the best clarity possible.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'The Lumia 925 also features Dolby Headphone audio enhancements to create a rich sound stage for your music and videos. You can also customize the sound with a seven-band graphic equalizer.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'The Lumia 928 includes access to signature Lumia apps including the complete set of the feature-rich, intuitive and customizable HERE experiences. HERE Maps, HERE Drive+, HERE Transit, and HERE City Lens help you navigate your life every day.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'Discover a world full of music and make it available anytime, anywhere with Nokia Music. With the Lumia 928, you''ll get instant access to millions of tracks of streaming internet radio, right out of the box for free and without interruptions from advertisements (data charges may apply). Download hours of music to your phone so you can play it when you are oine without a data connection or during a flight.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'AT&T boasts the largest 4G mobile broadband network in the United States, covering more than 292 million people with a combination of two layers of 4G technology: the 4G LTE (Long Term Evolution) network and an older technology called HSPA+ that delivers near-4G speeds. AT&T''s 4G LTE network is currently live in 261 markets across the U.S. (as of May, 2013) with more markets continually being added. AT&T expects to cover 300 million people with its 4G LTE network by the end of 2014.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'With 4G LTE technology, you''ll get mobile Internet speeds up to 10 times faster than 3G, enabling you to upload a photo in 6 seconds, download a song in 4 seconds, and download HD movies in minutes and apps almost instantly. You can expect average download data rates of 13 megabits per second (Mbps) and 6 Mbps for uploads in real-world, loaded network environments.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'If you are not in an area served by 4G LTE, you''ll be able to connect to AT&T''s HSPA+ enhanced backhaul network, which delivers speeds up to 4x faster than AT&T''s HSPA 3G network. With the combination of 4G LTE and HSPA+, you''ll enjoy higher data speed averages than other networks.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'In areas where either AT&T''s 3G or 4G network is not available, you''ll continue to receive service on the AT&T EDGE network, which offers availability in more than 13,000 US cities and along some 40,000 miles of major highways.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', 'Your Windows Phone comes alive with the things you care about -- people, places, songs, photos, and apps. It''s as personal and unique as you are, with Live Tiles for the people you care about and the apps you use all the time. And it works with Windows so you can access your documents and pictures from virtually anywhere via SkyDrive. Here''s just a sampling of what Windows 8 Phone is all about.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', '<strong>Live Tiles and Apps.</strong> You can pin people, apps, songs, Web sites, directions, games, photos, docs, and more to your Start Screen, and get real-time updates on everything you care about.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', '<strong>People Hub.</strong> Your Facebook, Outlook, LinkedIn, Twitter, Skype, and other contacts are accessible in People Hub. Instantly call, text, email or contact them using Skype all from the same place.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', '<strong>Rooms.</strong> An invitation-only place from where you can privately share a calendar, photo album, group chat, and notes with other room members.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', '<strong> SkyDrive.</strong> With SkyDrive all your photos, Word docs, Excel spread sheets and PowerPoint presentations are backed up and accessible virtually everywhere. SkyDrive comes with 7 GB of free storage space.'),
	('B00F3JPKCG', '<strong>Office and Email.</strong> The Office Hub is your go-to spot for Microsoft Word Mobile, PowerPoint Mobile, and Excel Mobile. And your email is clutter free, with multiple accounts (Outlook.com, Hotmail, Google Mail) in one Linked Inbox.'),
