	('0062447971', '<strong>CATHARINA INGELMAN-SUNDBERG</strong> is the Swedish author of over nineteen books. <em>The Little Old Lady Who Broke All the Rules</em> sold more than 1.2 million copies internationally and was a #1 bestseller in Canada. <em>The Little Old Lady Strikes Again</em> and <em>The Little Old Lady Behaving Badly</em> are also national bestsellers.'),
