	('1631363883', 'Sue Zipkin gains inspiration from the beauty of nature and things we don''t always see with our eyes but can feel with our hearts. She is inspired by the mysteries of the universe and the hidden worlds in everything. Textures and patterns found on flowers, insects, and dewdrops fascinate her. Zipkin''s art is the focal point of Amber Lotus''s Ram Dass calendar and greeting cards.'),
	('1781681201', '<b>Josh Ruebner</b>is the National Advocacy Director of the US Campaign to End the Israeli Occupation. He founded and directed Jews for Peace in Palestine and Israel, which merged with Jewish Voice for Peace. Ruebner was also a former Analyst in Middle East Affairs for the Congressional Research Service, a governmental agency providing members of Congress with policy analysis. He lives in Washington, DC.'),
